LIFE-LIKE PRODUCTS, INC., Appellant, v. SILBY-DOLCOURT CHEMICAL INDUSTRIES, INC., Appellee. No. 21652. United States Court of Appeals Fifth Circuit. Feb. 16, 1965. Albert J. Kramer, Washington, D. C., Thomas B. DeWolf and Helliwell, Mel-rose & DeWolf, Miami, Fla., for appellant. John Cyril Malloy, Miami, Fla., for appellee.

Before TUTTLE, Chief Judge, RIVES, Circuit Judge, and McRAE, District Judge.

PER CURIAM:

The judgment is affirmed on the findings and conclusions of the trial court.
